WEBVTT

00:03.320 --> 00:06.322
MAN: <i>Sometimes I dreamed about them.</i>

00:06.324 --> 00:09.158
<i>Other times it was
the smallest of things.</i>

00:10.970 --> 00:13.010
<i>The smell of fresh-cut grass.</i>

00:14.372 --> 00:16.491
<i>The rhythm of an early morning run.</i>

00:17.891 --> 00:20.470
<i>That's when the memories
came rushing back.</i>

00:21.884 --> 00:23.346
<i>There were four of us.</i>

00:24.242 --> 00:26.078
- Come on, Boots. 
- MAN: <i> Me and Gil...</i>

00:26.080 --> 00:26.943
- Is that all you got? 
- This isn't fair!

00:27.690 --> 00:30.967
MAN: <i>...Shawn and little Boots.</i>

00:31.400 --> 00:32.398
Shawn, let's go,

00:32.400 --> 00:33.250
<i>we got to catch 'em!</i>

00:33.913 --> 00:35.655
MAN: <i>There was also a girl.</i>

00:38.907 --> 00:39.921
<i>Jessie.</i>

00:41.396 --> 00:42.939
<i>We were all best friends.</i>

00:44.416 --> 00:47.114
♪ ♪

00:49.218 --> 00:50.550
Hurry up, Boots!

00:50.552 --> 00:52.239
Fire in the hole!

00:52.588 --> 00:53.854
All right...

00:53.856 --> 00:55.422
(loud popping)

00:55.424 --> 00:57.958
(whooping)

00:57.960 --> 00:59.993
- (whistling, popping)
- Nice one, Gil!

00:59.995 --> 01:01.561
(whoops)

01:01.563 --> 01:04.131
- (laughs)
- (popping)

01:04.132 --> 01:05.632
Jackson, what are you doing?

01:05.634 --> 01:07.601
Guys, you dare me to jump?

01:07.603 --> 01:08.935
- No.
- Jackie, no way.

01:08.937 --> 01:10.203
The water's, like, 30 degrees.

01:10.205 --> 01:12.005
So what?

01:12.007 --> 01:13.707
- I'm gonna do it.
- No, you're not.

01:13.709 --> 01:15.475
- He's not gonna do it.
- That's crazy.

01:15.477 --> 01:17.144
Chicken on the high board!

01:17.146 --> 01:18.945
(clucks)

01:18.947 --> 01:21.648
♪ ♪

01:21.650 --> 01:22.783
Holy balls!

01:22.785 --> 01:25.185
♪ You can't stop my heart ♪

01:25.187 --> 01:26.219
- No way!
- ♪ From turning ♪

01:26.221 --> 01:27.587
- ♪ Inside out ♪
- Oh, my God!

01:27.589 --> 01:29.156
I knew he'd do it.

01:29.158 --> 01:30.624
- (whooping)
- Yeah!

01:31.756 --> 01:32.934
JACKSON: <i>We were just a bunch</i>

01:32.936 --> 01:34.647
<i>-of innocent kids</i><i>from Brennan</i>
- (whoops) Yeah!

01:34.649 --> 01:36.096
<i>having the time of our lives.</i>

01:36.998 --> 01:38.431
(whooping)

01:39.425 --> 01:41.500
<i>We had no idea what was coming.</i>

01:41.502 --> 01:42.735
JESSIE: <i>Mom, stop!</i>

01:42.737 --> 01:44.103
WOMAN: Get in the car!

01:44.105 --> 01:45.404
Mom, you're drunk, you can't drive!

01:45.406 --> 01:47.106
- Shut your...
- You're drunk, Mom!

01:47.108 --> 01:48.941
- Stop it! Jackson!
- Get in the car!

01:48.943 --> 01:50.847
WOMAN: You are getting baptized
today, no matter what!

01:50.872 --> 01:51.631
Jackson!

01:51.633 --> 01:53.045
You get out of this car, you're
getting the hairbrush again.

01:53.047 --> 01:55.181
- Do you understand me?
- (car door slams)

01:55.183 --> 01:57.817
Let her out! You let her out!

01:57.819 --> 01:59.310
You are the whole
reason she needs Jesus!

01:59.335 --> 01:59.919
You can't drive!

01:59.921 --> 02:02.021
Do you understand me? You are drunk.

02:02.023 --> 02:04.356
You can't drive... give me the keys!

02:04.358 --> 02:05.782
Don't you... Get your hands off of me!

02:05.807 --> 02:06.759
You're drunk, you can't drive!

02:06.761 --> 02:09.360
Get out of my way! You little bastard!

02:09.363 --> 02:11.297
Get in the car! Get in!

02:11.299 --> 02:12.631
Get in! Get in, get in!

02:12.633 --> 02:14.734
Little bastard!

02:14.736 --> 02:16.635
- Don't you dare!
- (engine starts)

02:16.637 --> 02:18.771
Unlock the door, unlock this door!

02:18.773 --> 02:20.606
Don't you dare take off

02:20.608 --> 02:22.241
with my daughter! No!

02:22.243 --> 02:24.910
What do you think you're doing?

02:24.912 --> 02:26.419
No, get out of the car,

02:26.444 --> 02:28.224
- get out of the car!
- (laughing)

02:28.318 --> 02:30.985
I'm gonna beat you so
bad! You will never

02:30.987 --> 02:33.021
see my daughter again!

02:33.797 --> 02:35.206
Psycho.

02:35.231 --> 02:36.909
I cannot believe this...
when'd you learn how to drive?

02:36.911 --> 02:38.893
I didn't. I have no idea what I'm doing.

02:39.658 --> 02:41.129
Guys, we did it.

02:41.131 --> 02:43.564
Everybody in. One, two, three...

02:43.566 --> 02:44.799
- Bellflower Boys!
- (shrieks)

02:44.801 --> 02:46.567
- Yeah!
- (whooping)

02:46.569 --> 02:48.169
- Yeah! Yeah!
- (on radio): ♪ Break it up ♪

02:48.171 --> 02:50.138
Yeah!

02:50.140 --> 02:52.874
ALL: ♪ Pour some sugar on me ♪

02:52.876 --> 02:54.909
♪ Oh, in the name of love ♪

02:54.911 --> 02:56.077
♪ Pour some... ♪

02:56.079 --> 02:58.713
♪ Sugar on me ♪

02:58.715 --> 03:00.448
♪ Come on, fire me up ♪

03:00.450 --> 03:03.284
- ♪ Pour some sugar on me ♪
- (whooping, screaming)

03:03.286 --> 03:05.820
♪ I can't get enough ♪

03:05.822 --> 03:07.221
- Are these your mom's?
- Yeah.

